div.div:
NOTES :
1. Currently only Chrome browser is supported
2. AudioWorkletProcessor that provided continuous stream of raw mic data, generates glitches in some mobile phones. Until this issue is fixed, we use MediaRecorder that records mic data and makes them available when MediaRecorder is stopped. Every five minutes, MediaRecorder is stopped and started again immediately.
3. When stopped button is pressed, the data that are already processed, are presented to user for a smooth UI experience.
Worst case scenario, (user presses Stop button just before MediaRecorder is stopped && inference of the previous 5 min segment is not completed), our analysis misses the last 10 min before Stop button is pressed
